Class DailyLoadProfile

  • java.lang.Object
    • amesmarket.DailyLoadProfile

  • public class DailyLoadProfile
extends java.lang.Object
    Model the load profile for a particular day. Hours are 0 indexed. A standard day goes from 0 to 23.
